
This directory contains workflow of running multi_hosts_multi_emulators_demo
To run with agent script, instruction and steps are the same as in multi_hosts_demo other than
run worker_multi_emulator.py instead of workerserver.py
=================================================================================

Master VM:
run: python masterserver.py <path of args.txt>

args.txt example:
[settings]
app_apk_path = /Users/hewei/app-debug.apk
test_apk_path = /Users/hewei/app-debug-androidTest.apk

The work_dir is "/mto_work_dir" under home_dir, agent scripts deployed to Azure vm
creates work_dir if not exists, to run script standalone, mto_work_dir need to exists.

=================================================================================

Worker VMs:
run worker_multi_emulator.py
path of args.txt should be its corresponding path.

=================================================================================
User end:
scp directory1/filename1 username@masterserver VM1:directory2
(scp <path to work_file.zip> < path to new_job_flag> username@masterserver:~/mto_work_dir)
Run: "python user.py <path to args.txt>" to connect to master server and fetch results.

=================================================================================

